description: Every day many people come to Prague as tourists. Also many Czech people. There´s nothing unusual about it. But when I met this youngster telling me that he came to Prague for sightseeing I immediately became suspicious. He was from quiet far away, from South-Bohemia. And he was quite open-minded. I was surprised that this guy, a car-mechanic, seemed to have experienced a lot already. Well, I asked him a bit about his situation, about his wage and expenses and I finally came to the conclusion that it might make sense to make an offer to him. But how far would he go?
title: Czech Hunter 130
